snippet.textDisplay:
When you are listening to Coke Studio and you see produced by Rohail Hyatt, then you just have plug in your earphones and close your eyes, you'll find yourself in another state of mind after 2-3 minutes. 
And top of that, it has the voice of Hadiqa Kiani, it will definitely go on repeat mode.
😍😘
